ontentItem"><div class="ContentItem-main"><div class="ContentItem-image"><a class="TopicLink" href="//www.zhihu.com/topic/20060030" target="_blank"><div class="Popover"><div id="null-toggle" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" aria-owns="null-content"><img class="Avatar Avatar--large TopicLink-avatar" width="60" height="60" src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-02503af67a59f8d4e4e6079a70747fb2_im.jpg" srcSet="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-02503af67a59f8d4e4e6079a70747fb2_xl.jpg 2x" alt="AirPods"/></div></div></a></div><div class="ContentItem-head"><h2 class="ContentItem-title"><a class="TopicLink" href="//www.zhihu.com/topic/20060030" target="_blank"><div class="Popover"><div id="null-toggle" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" aria-owns="null-content">AirPods</div></div></a></h2></div></div></div></div><div class="List-item"><div class="List-itemMeta"><div class="ActivityItem-meta"><span class="ActivityItem-metaTitle">回答了问题</span><span>1 个月前</span></div></div><div class="ContentItem AnswerItem" data-zop="{&quot;authorName&quot;:&quot;flyerye&quot;,&quot;itemId&quot;:493289587,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;股票多因子模型中大家都是如何筛选因子的？&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;answer&quot;}" name="493289587" itemProp="answer" itemType="http://schema.org/Answer" itemscope=""><h2 class="ContentItem-title"><div itemProp="zhihu:question" itemType="http://schema.org/Question" itemscope=""><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.zhihu.com/question/292308387"/><meta itemProp="name" content="股票多因子模型中大家都是如何筛选因子的？"/><a target="_blank" data-za-detail-view-element_name="Title" href="/question/292308387/answer/493289587">股票多因子模型中大家都是如何筛选因子的？</a></div></h2><div class="ContentItem-meta"><div class="AuthorInfo AnswerItem-authorInfo" itemProp="author" itemscope="" itemType="http://schema.org/Person"><meta itemProp="name" content="flyerye"/><meta itemProp="image" content="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-faae79f199b964c3ae6219775a969b5f_s.jpg"/><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.zhihu.com/people/flyerye"/><meta itemProp="zhihu:followerCount"/><span class="UserLink AuthorInfo-avatarWrapper"><div class="Popover"><div id="null-toggle" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" aria-owns="null-content"><a class="UserLink-link" data-za-detail-view-element_name="User" target="_blank" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/flyerye"><img class="Avatar AuthorInfo-avatar" width="38" height="38" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-faae79f199b964c3ae6219775a969b5f_xs.jpg" srcSet="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-faae79f199b964c3ae6219775a969b5f_l.jpg 2x" alt="flyerye"/></a></div></div></span><div class="AuthorInfo-content"><div class="AuthorInfo-head"><span class="UserLink AuthorInfo-name"><div class="Popover"><div id="null-toggle" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" aria-owns="null-content"><a class="UserLink-link" data-za-detail-view-element_name="User" target="_blank" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/flyerye">flyerye</a></div></div></span></div><div class="AuthorInfo-detail"><div class="AuthorInfo-badge"><div class="RichText ztext AuthorInfo-badgeText">游走在数据缝隙间的宽客</div></div></div></div></div><div class="AnswerItem-extraInfo"><span class="Voters"><button type="button" class="Button Button--plain">1 人<!-- -->赞同了该回答</button></span></div></div><meta itemProp="image" content=""/><meta itemProp="upvoteCount" content="1"/><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.zhihu.com/question/292308387/answer/493289587"/><meta itemProp="dateCreated" content="2018-09-17T09:47:23.000Z"/><meta itemProp="dateModified" content="2018-09-17T09:47:23.000Z"/><meta itemProp="commentCount" content="0"/><div class="RichContent is-collapsed"><div class="RichContent-inner"><span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemProp="text">这关键取决于你对每个因子的理解。首先因子会有属性的偏向性，比如因子可以归类到，动量类，价值类，市场情绪类等。每一类因子都有它自己的特性。比如，动量类因子基于量价类的数据，换手（相对价值类）高，高收益同时伴随高波动，在牛市（动量）或者高波动（反转）市场表现好。价值类因子更看重一个公司的长期价值，换手（相对）低，收益稳定，在价值风格偏向明显（2017年）的时期表现好。因此，我们在分析一个因子的时候，不能…</span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-more Button--plain">阅读全文<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowDown ContentItem-arrowIcon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 13L8.285 9.218a.758.758 0 0 0-1.064 0 .738.738 0 0 0 0 1.052l4.249 4.512a.758.758 0 0 0 1.064 0l4.246-4.512a.738.738 0 0 0 0-1.052.757.757 0 0 0-1.063 0L12.002 13z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></div><div class="ContentItem-actions"><span><button aria-label="赞同" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--up"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleUp VoteButton-TriangleUp" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M2 18.242c0-.326.088-.532.237-.896l7.98-13.203C10.572 3.57 11.086 3 12 3c.915 0 1.429.571 1.784 1.143l7.98 13.203c.15.364.236.57.236.896 0 1.386-.875 1.9-1.955 1.9H3.955c-1.08 0-1.955-.517-1.955-1.9z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span>赞同 <!-- -->1</button><button aria-label="反对" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--down"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleDown" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M20.044 3H3.956C2.876 3 2 3.517 2 4.9c0 .326.087.533.236.896L10.216 19c.355.571.87 1.143 1.784 1.143s1.429-.572 1.784-1.143l7.98-13.204c.149-.363.236-.57.236-.896 0-1.386-.876-1.9-1.956-1.9z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-action Button--plain Button--withIcon Button--withLabel"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--Comment Button-zi" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="1.2em" height="1.2em"><path d="M10.241 19.313a.97.97 0 0 0-.77.2 7.908 7.908 0 0 1-3.772 1.482.409.409 0 0 1-.38-.637 5.825 5.825 0 0 0 1.11-2.237.605.605 0 0 0-.227-.59A7.935 7.935 0 0 1 3 11.25C3 6.7 7.03 3 12 3s9 3.7 9 8.25-4.373 9.108-10.759 8.063z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span>添加评